airModulesJSONTemplate.journeyType: (function() { if(clientDataObj.data.journeyTypeOption == "ow" || clientDataObj.data.journeyType == "ONE_WAY" || clientDataObj.data.journeyType == "ow"){ return "ONE_WAY" } else if (clientDataObj.data.journeyTypeOption == "rt" || clientDataObj.data.journeyType == "ROUND_TRIP" || clientDataObj.data.journeyType == "rt"){ return "ROUND_TRIP" } else { return null }})()
airModulesJSONTemplate.departureDate: (function(){ var departureDate = clientDataObj.data.departureDate && clientDataObj.data.departureDate != -1 && clientDataObj.data.departureDate != "n/a"?new Date(clientDataObj.data.departureDate):clientDataObj.data.departure && clientDataObj.data.departure != -1 && clientDataObj.data.departure != "n/a"? new Date(clientDataObj.data.departure): null; if(departureDate != null) {return departureDate.getFullYear() +'-'+('0'+(departureDate.getMonth()+1)).slice(-2)+'-'+('0'+departureDate.getDate()).slice(-2)} else return departureDate;})()
airModulesJSONTemplate.returnDate: (function(){ var returnDate = clientDataObj.data.returnDate && clientDataObj.data.returnDate != -1 && clientDataObj.data.returnDate != "n/a"?new Date(clientDataObj.data.returnDate):clientDataObj.data.return && clientDataObj.data.return != -1 && clientDataObj.data.return != "n/a"? new Date(clientDataObj.data.return): null; if(returnDate != null) {return returnDate.getFullYear() +'-'+('0'+(returnDate.getMonth()+1)).slice(-2)+'-'+('0'+returnDate.getDate()).slice(-2)} else return returnDate;})()
airModulesJSONTemplate.tripLength: formattedAirModulesJSON.departureDate != null && formattedAirModulesJSON.returnDate != null? Math.round(Math.abs((new Date(formattedAirModulesJSON.departureDate).getTime() - new Date(formattedAirModulesJSON.returnDate).getTime())/(86400000))):null
